Package oracle.cloud.storage.model

Class Summary
Container This class represents a handle to a Container in a Service Instance of the Oracle Storage Cloud Service.
ContentRange Class for specifying content ranges used in storage object retrieval.
Key A Key represents a handle to a storage object.
QueryResult Holds the results of a query operation.
StorageInputMultistream Present multiple content ranges as a single contiguous stream
StorageInputStream This class is used to retrieve Storage Objects from the service instance.
 

Enum Summary
AclType Represents an ACL Type.
QueryOption This enum represents the supported query options.
